cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is likely to belong to the category of "Computation and Language" (cs.CL) as it deals with speech-to-text translation and language modeling. It could also belong to "Sound" (cs.SD) as it deals with speech recognition. "Machine Learning" (cs.LG) and "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI) are also possible categories as the paper discusses the use of pre-training and fine-tuning of models. "Social and Information Networks" (cs.SI) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with improving low-resource language translation.
